#### Step 2: Pilih GK (Budget: $95)
```
1. HAFIZIE AZIZAN - $50 (Main)
2. AMIR AZMI - $45 (Bench)
Total spent: $95
Remaining: $905
```

#### Step 3: Pilih DF (Budget: $290)
```
