## ğŸ”„ Tukar Formation Tengah Game

Cuba tukar dari **4-4-2** ke **4-3-3**:

**Before (4-4-2)**:
- Starting: 1 GK, 4 DF, 4 MF, 2 ST
- Bench: 1 GK, 3 outfield

**Click 4-3-3**

**After (4-3-3)**:
- Starting: 1 GK, 4 DF, 3 MF, 3 ST
- Bench: 1 GK, 1 MF, 2 outfield

Changes:
- 1 MF masuk bench (kurang 1 MF slot)
- 1 ST dari bench masuk main (dapat 1 ST slot)

